<h3>A method to check if the scrutiny period calculation can proceed.</h3>

<p>This method also creates the start date, day count, procedure and calculation style as instance variables.</p>

<pre><code><a href='https://github.com/ukparliament/egg-timer/blob/main/app/controllers/calculator_controller.rb#L419' title='View on GitHub'>419</a>   def calculation_can_proceed?( start_date, day_count, procedure, calculation_style )</code></pre>
<p>We create a variable to hold a boolean, determining if the scrutiny period calculation can proceed.</p>

<pre><code><a href='https://github.com/ukparliament/egg-timer/blob/main/app/controllers/calculator_controller.rb#L422' title='View on GitHub'>422</a>     calculation_can_proceed = true</code></pre>
<p>We create an array to hold any errors we find as a result of missing information.</p>

<pre><code><a href='https://github.com/ukparliament/egg-timer/blob/main/app/controllers/calculator_controller.rb#L425' title='View on GitHub'>425</a>     @missing_information = []</code></pre>
<h2>We check for the presence of a valid start date.</h2>

<p>If the start date is present ...</p>

<pre><code><a href='https://github.com/ukparliament/egg-timer/blob/main/app/controllers/calculator_controller.rb#L429' title='View on GitHub'>429</a>     if start_date</code></pre>
<p>... we attempt to convert the start date string into a date, storing the result as a instance variable.</p>

<pre><code><a href='https://github.com/ukparliament/egg-timer/blob/main/app/controllers/calculator_controller.rb#L432' title='View on GitHub'>432</a>       begin</code></pre>
<pre><code><a href='https://github.com/ukparliament/egg-timer/blob/main/app/controllers/calculator_controller.rb#L433' title='View on GitHub'>433</a>          @start_date = Date.parse( start_date )</code></pre>
<p>If the start date string cannot be converted into a date ...</p>

<pre><code><a href='https://github.com/ukparliament/egg-timer/blob/main/app/controllers/calculator_controller.rb#L436' title='View on GitHub'>436</a>       rescue ArgumentError</code></pre>
<p>... we flag that the calculation cannot proceed ...</p>

<pre><code><a href='https://github.com/ukparliament/egg-timer/blob/main/app/controllers/calculator_controller.rb#L439' title='View on GitHub'>439</a>         calculation_can_proceed = false</code></pre>
<p>... and add a reason to the missing information array.</p>

<pre><code><a href='https://github.com/ukparliament/egg-timer/blob/main/app/controllers/calculator_controller.rb#L442' title='View on GitHub'>442</a>         @missing_information &lt;&lt; invalid_date_type_label</code></pre>
<pre><code><a href='https://github.com/ukparliament/egg-timer/blob/main/app/controllers/calculator_controller.rb#L443' title='View on GitHub'>443</a>       end</code></pre>
<p>Otherwise, if the start date is not present ...</p>

<pre><code><a href='https://github.com/ukparliament/egg-timer/blob/main/app/controllers/calculator_controller.rb#L446' title='View on GitHub'>446</a>     else</code></pre>
<p>... we flag that the calculation cannot proceed ...</p>

<pre><code><a href='https://github.com/ukparliament/egg-timer/blob/main/app/controllers/calculator_controller.rb#L449' title='View on GitHub'>449</a>       calculation_can_proceed = false</code></pre>
<p>... and add a reason to the missing information array.</p>

<pre><code><a href='https://github.com/ukparliament/egg-timer/blob/main/app/controllers/calculator_controller.rb#L452' title='View on GitHub'>452</a>       @missing_information &lt;&lt; missing_date_type_label</code></pre>
<pre><code><a href='https://github.com/ukparliament/egg-timer/blob/main/app/controllers/calculator_controller.rb#L453' title='View on GitHub'>453</a>     end</code></pre>
<h2>We check for the presence of a valid day count.</h2>

<p>If a day count has been passed ...</p>

<pre><code><a href='https://github.com/ukparliament/egg-timer/blob/main/app/controllers/calculator_controller.rb#L457' title='View on GitHub'>457</a>     if day_count</code></pre>
<p>... we convert the day count to an integer, storing the result as a instance variable.</p>

<pre><code><a href='https://github.com/ukparliament/egg-timer/blob/main/app/controllers/calculator_controller.rb#L460' title='View on GitHub'>460</a>       @day_count = day_count.to_i</code></pre>
<p>If the day count is an invalid day count ...</p>

<pre><code><a href='https://github.com/ukparliament/egg-timer/blob/main/app/controllers/calculator_controller.rb#L463' title='View on GitHub'>463</a>       if is_day_count_invalid?( @day_count )</code></pre>
<p>... we do not flag that the calculation cannot proceed because this will be picked up by the day count form.</p>

<p>We add a reason to the missing information array.</p>

<pre><code><a href='https://github.com/ukparliament/egg-timer/blob/main/app/controllers/calculator_controller.rb#L468' title='View on GitHub'>468</a>         @missing_information &lt;&lt; &#39;a valid day count&#39;</code></pre>
<pre><code><a href='https://github.com/ukparliament/egg-timer/blob/main/app/controllers/calculator_controller.rb#L469' title='View on GitHub'>469</a>       end</code></pre>
<p>Otherwise, if a day count has not been passed ...</p>

<pre><code><a href='https://github.com/ukparliament/egg-timer/blob/main/app/controllers/calculator_controller.rb#L472' title='View on GitHub'>472</a>     else</code></pre>
<p>... we do not flag that the calculation cannot proceed because this will be picked up by the day count form.</p>

<p>We add a reason to the missing information array.</p>

<pre><code><a href='https://github.com/ukparliament/egg-timer/blob/main/app/controllers/calculator_controller.rb#L477' title='View on GitHub'>477</a>       @missing_information &lt;&lt; &#39;a day count&#39;</code></pre>
<pre><code><a href='https://github.com/ukparliament/egg-timer/blob/main/app/controllers/calculator_controller.rb#L478' title='View on GitHub'>478</a>     end</code></pre>
<h2>We check for the presence of a valid procedure <em>or</em> a valid calculation style.</h2>

<p>If the calculation has been passed neither a procedure, nor a calculation style ...</p>

<pre><code><a href='https://github.com/ukparliament/egg-timer/blob/main/app/controllers/calculator_controller.rb#L482' title='View on GitHub'>482</a>     if !procedure and !calculation_style</code></pre>
<p>... we flag that the calculation cannot proceed ...</p>

